vs a champ with
{{item:3742}} {{item:3068}} {{item:3047}} {{item:3143}} {{item:3110}} {{item:3075}} 
is gonna be like a 450 ad champ hitting a champ with 150 armor. this alone means that their autos will do something like 200 and thornmail will do half that back before you even consider what the tank is gonna do to them. it would take at least 3 lethality stackers to take one down in a reasonable amount of time. The reason adc used to build crit attack speed and ad is because if you combined it you can out scale the tank stats. with just penetration you get out scaled.
